OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774868573
OL,3,CCapital city to introduce tourism tax
OL,4,Cfor overnight stays from 2027
OL,6,FA new visitor levy will be introduced
OL,7,Ffor overnight stays in Cardiff after
OL,8,Fthe plans were approved by the city's
OL,9,Ffull council.
OL,11,FThe scheme follows new Welsh
OL,12,Flegislation, which received Royal
OL,13,FAssent in September 2025, allowing
OL,14,Fcouncils across Wales to charge a fee
OL,15,Fon overnight visitors from April 2027.
OL,17,FThe decision comes after a public
OL,18,Fconsultation that drew nearly 2,000
OL,19,Fresponses. Of those, 62% supported the
OL,20,Fproposal, while 33% were opposed and
OL,21,F5% were neutral.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
