PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774868573
OL,3,CCapital city to introduce tourism tax
OL,4,Cfor overnight stays from 2027
OL,6,FSupporters said similar charges are
OL,7,Fcommon in other major cities and could
OL,8,Fhelp fund improvements to tourism and
OL,9,Fmanage the impact of large events.
OL,10,FHowever, concerns were raised about
OL,11,Fthe potential effect on visitor
OL,12,Fnumbers, added pressure on
OL,13,Faccommodation providers, and how the
OL,14,Fmoney would be spent.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
