PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774868573
OL,3,CCapital city to introduce tourism tax
OL,4,Cfor overnight stays from 2027
OL,6,FUnder the scheme, visitors staying in
OL,7,Fmost types of accommodation will pay
OL,8,F#1.30 per person, per night. A reduced
OL,9,Frate of 75p will apply to campsites
OL,10,Fand shared accommodation such as
OL,11,Fhostels. The levy will apply to stays
OL,12,Fof up to 31 nights and will be subject
OL,13,Fto VAT where applicable.
OL,15,FSome exemptions will be in place,
OL,16,Fincluding for people staying longer
OL,17,Fthan 31 nights, those in emergency or
OL,18,Ftemporary accommodation arranged by
OL,19,Fthe council, and under-18s staying in
OL,20,Fhostels or campsites.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
