PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774868573
OL,3,CCapital city to introduce tourism tax
OL,4,Cfor overnight stays from 2027
OL,6,FThe levy is expected to raise around
OL,7,F#3.5 million a year. The money will be
OL,8,Fcollected by the Welsh Revenue
OL,9,FAuthority and passed on to the
OL,10,Fcouncil. A new partnership forum is
OL,11,Fset to be established to advise on how
OL,12,Fthe funds are used, with a focus on
OL,13,Fsupporting the visitor economy.
OL,15,FThe council says it will continue
OL,16,Fworking with tourism businesses ahead
OL,17,Fof the scheme's introduction in April
OL,18,F2027.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
